---
import DocsPage from '../../layouts/DocsPage.astro';
---

<DocsPage title="Model Prism — Overview" description="Open Model Prism: multi-tenant OpenAI-compatible LLM gateway with intelligent routing and cost tracking.">

  <div class="mb-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <img src="/model-prism-logo.svg" width="32" height="32" alt="Model Prism" class="h-8 w-8" />
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Model Prism</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-lg">
      Open Model Prism is a multi-tenant OpenAI-compatible LLM gateway with intelligent routing, cost tracking, and self-optimizing model selection. Connect multiple LLM providers, route requests to the optimal model, track costs per team, and let the built-in Benchmark Agent continuously fine-tune routing quality based on real production data.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature cards -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mb-2">Multi-Provider</h3>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Connect OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, Azure, Bedrock, OpenRouter, vLLM, and any OpenAI-compatible endpoint simultaneously.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mb-2">Intelligent Routing</h3>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Send <code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">model: "auto"</code> and let the routing engine classify requests into 45 categories and select the optimal model.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mb-2">Cost Tracking</h3>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Per-request cost calculation, daily aggregates, baseline vs actual comparisons, and real-time dashboards showing savings from intelligent routing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mb-2">Multi-Tenant</h3>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Isolated gateway endpoints per team with their own API keys, rate limits, model access controls, and routing configuration.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#818cf8]/20 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90">Self-Optimizing Routing</h3>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-500/15 text-green-400 border border-green-500/25">New</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">The built-in Benchmark Agent analyzes every routing decision against actual outcomes. It detects over-routing and under-routing patterns, then adjusts thresholds, keyword rules, and model priorities — with mandatory dry-run simulation before any change goes live. Set it up once, and routing quality improves automatically over time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#818cf8]/20 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90">Session Tracking</h3>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-500/15 text-green-400 border border-green-500/25">New</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Group related requests into sessions via the <code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">x-session-id</code> header. Track conversational coherence, analyze session-level cost and quality, and export structured activity dumps for AI-driven evaluation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#818cf8]/20 bg-[#0d0d14] p-5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90">Built-in WebChat</h3>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-500/15 text-green-400 border border-green-500/25">New</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Chat with any available model directly from the admin UI. Lightweight SSE streaming (no WebSockets required), model selection dropdown with auto-routing as default, and real-time routing info badges showing which model was selected, category, tier, and confidence.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick links -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-6">Documentation</h2>
  <div class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/model-prism/getting-started" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-[#0d0d14] px-5 py-4 hover:border-[#38bdf8]/30 hover:bg-[#38bdf8]/5 transition-all duration-200 group">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-[#38bdf8] transition-colors">Getting Started</h3>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-0.5">Installation, setup wizard, first tenant, and gateway usage.</p>
      </div>
